

Spring mvc with maven project


for controllers mvc annotations - used spring-webmvc jar
for getter setters tostring - used lombok
for converting jsp pages to servlet - used tomcat jasper

used tomcat 10.1.8

web.xml contains details of dispacther-servlet (tharun.xml)
dispacther-servlet acts as a front end controller
dispacther-servlet contains InternalResourceViewResolver

in deployment assembly jsp file location should be added